      "created_at": "2016-10-06T14:06:55.136Z",
      "cooked": "<p>te lumte admin ! -kisha besim ne aftesite e tua, “nothing is imposible”.<img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/joy.png?v=5\" title=\":joy:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":joy:\"></p>\n<p>-ke nje shishe vere nga te Pjerit… perndryshe kur te vij vet ne Albanie,  <em>do te shperblehesh !</em>.<img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/stuck_out_tongue.png?v=5\" title=\":stuck_out_tongue:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":stuck_out_tongue:\"></p>",
